  <brief_title>Heart Rate Variability in Extracorporeal Membrane Oxygenation (ECMO) Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Clinical Application of Multimodal Physiological Signal Analysis in Critical Ill Patients Depending on Extracorporeal Membrane Oxygenation</official_title>
